des:
This is the official Alexa skill for the City of Lake Forest California.You can ask questions like:

'What jobs are open?'

'How do i report graffiti?'

'What parks have tennis courts?'

'What is the phone number for skate park?'

'What is the address of city hall?'

If you ask a question and don't get an answer, your question will be saved and you can stop back later to get your answer.
